# Git sync (two computers)

This repo syncs through GitHub (`MoonlitJadeRabbit.github.io`).

**Before editing:** run `git pull origin main --rebase` (or `.\scripts\sync-github.ps1 -Action Pull`). Cursor hooks also pull on new messages.

**Do not auto-commit or auto-push.** Only commit and push when the user explicitly asks (e.g. "commit and push").

If pull fails (offline, merge conflict), say so briefly and do not force-push.
